---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="页面走丢啦">
  <section class="py-24 text-center relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 pointer-events-none flex items-center justify-center">
      <div class="font-serif font-black text-paper-200/50 text-[18rem] leading-none select-none">404</div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-8xl mb-6 inline-block animate-wobble-in">🍊</div>
    <p class="font-hand text-3xl text-paper-600 mb-2">oops...</p>
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-ink-900 mb-3">页面走丢啦</h1>
    <p class="text-ink-500 mb-10 max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      小橙子在果园里找不到这个页面，也许它被风吹走了？
      <br />
      要不咱们回到起点重新出发吧 ～
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-3 justify-center flex-wrap">
      <a href="/" class="btn-primary btn-shine">
        <span>←</span><span>回到首页</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/blog" class="btn-ghost">
        <span>📖</span><span>去看看文章</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
